<td bgcolor=#ffffff>



<tt>&lt;user&gt;</tt> is defined in the <i>Main RXML parser</i> module.
<p>
Prints information about the specified user. By default, the full name
of the user and her e-mail address will be printed, with a mailto link
and link to the home page of that user.

<p>The <tt>&lt;user&gt;</tt> tag requires an <i>Authentification</i> module
to work.


<br clear=all>
<img src=/internal-roxen-unit width=1 height=10 alt="">

</td>
</tr>
</table>


