<font color=white>Attributes</font>
</td>
<td bgcolor=#ffffff>
<img src=/internal-roxen-unit width=100% height=1 alt=""></td>
</tr>
<tr>

<td bgcolor=#ffffff colspan=2>






<a href="#name">name</a>,
<a href="#realname">realname</a>,
<a href="#email">email</a>,
<a href="#link">link</a>,
<a href="#nolink">nolink</a>,
&nbsp;

</td>
</tr>
</table>


</td>
</tr>
</table>






































<p>
<b><font color=#113377 size=+2 >Attributes</font></b>



<dl>

<p><dt><tt><b><a name="name">name</a></b></tt>

<dd>
The login name of the user.



<p><dt><tt><b><a name="realname">realname</a></b></tt>

<dd>
Only print the full name of the user, with no link.



<p><dt><tt><b><a name="email">email</a></b></tt>

<dd>
Only print the e-mail address of the user, with no link.



<p><dt><tt><b><a name="link">link</a></b></tt>

<dd>
Include links. Only meaningful together with the <tt>realname</tt>
or <tt>email</tt> attribute.



<p><dt><tt><b><a name="nolink">nolink</a></b></tt>

<dd>
Don't include the links.



</dl>










